id

Serial number of subject. Coming from two datasets, these numbers may not be unique for each person. In order to destinguish subjects use code.

submit date

T1_submitdate: Date and time when online questionnaire was submitted.

date stamp

T1_datestamp: Date and time of last activity. Equals T1_submitdate, when questinnaire was successfully finished.

start date

T1_startdate: Date and time when online questionnaire was started.
